## ðŸŒŸ Features

- **SARN Layers** â€” Top-k activated sparse neurons with rewiring
- **Neuron Growth** â€” Dynamically adds neurons when novelty is detected
- **Hebbian Plasticity** â€” Rewires weights based on usage strength
- **Fully Modular** â€” Build networks with any size, connection config, and activation

